thread.title: Tech Data Corporation Announces Dates For Its First Quarter Earnings Release And Annual Meeting Of Shareholders

author: cnbc.com
title: Tech Data Corporation Announces Dates For Its First Quarter Earnings Release And Annual Meeting Of Shareholders
text:
CLEARWATER, Fla., May 10, 2018 /PRNewswire/ -- Tech Data (NASDAQ: TECD) today announced the following information regarding the release of its first quarter fiscal year 2019 results and the Company's Annual Meeting of Shareholders.
First Quarter Fiscal Year 2019 results:
Thursday, May 31, 2018 – Tech Data will announce its first quarter fiscal year 2019 results before the market opens and will host an investor conference call and webcast at 9:00 a.m. ET.
The live conference call will be available by dialing 877-407-3980 from the U.S. or 201-689-8475 from outside the U.S. The earnings press release and supporting materials, as well as a link to an audio webcast of the conference call, will be available at www.techdata.com/investor . A replay of the conference call will be available one hour after completion of the call.
Annual Meeting of Shareholders:
Wednesday, June 6, 2018 – Tech Data will hold its Annual Meeting of Shareholders at the Company's headquarters in Clearwater, FL, on Wednesday, June 6, 2018, at 3:00 p.m. ET.
A live audio webcast of the Annual Meeting will be accessible at www.techdata.com/investor with a replay available one hour after completion of the meeting.
About Tech Data
Tech Data connects the world with the power of technology. Our end-to-end portfolio of products, services and solutions, highly specialized skills, and expertise in next-generation technologies enable channel partners to bring to market the products and solutions the world needs to connect, grow and advance. Tech Data is ranked No. 107 on the Fortune 500® and has been named one of Fortune's "World's Most Admired Companies" for nine straight years. To find out more, visit www.techdata.com or follow us on Twitter, LinkedIn, and Facebook.
